[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering data formatting**\n\nI'm thinking about how I can deal with long JSON lines. It seems like I could prefix each line with `data: {`, but I realize that may not work for value concatenation in the event. For Server-Sent Events (SSE), multiple data lines are joined by a newline, so maybe it's best to keep everything compact. I wonder if I need to check line lengths. Even though they can be long, string concatenation could simplify things. But formatting with `.replace(\"\\n\",\"\")` might also keep it readable.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0a608b3e6a69a970016a3ef4b07a608194849924a86396ac18\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqPvTCSKq_5XTx3OSlgZYaQB_DLYBwukG78x5twWiOIoTR0ICoQBFiX8DFr38DQRyHdoLUwFAZ_M7IZRS5RYUDpZY09ICZJo70kyRK2G3GWMgTELcDZDXNqF_2IsEgF9ewKoClzZFviUA1PFaV5dZL2lSkcoLf78AT0lV6JWwe-nyIHUQB2PVrDmLhAjNVmY8_m_5r09-fseMKxuuqox8EtDY5rCU9XIwYSVay6TEzVvvhaZPMoJtZS_bI_2yw3tKaeNsFA87aRthnxQW_DA6FKd-pJSfkyq8CBkPQYk4kjpzllHe7JA2BJ1xJbtHpAQLPMmunQ0wxOTnkSeAtN3PM4hrwWXWYzaMAkwKIBFajdqBOb2tixuvbM5t9mSJq81FGGI4DSWqUyyjMAJktjl2EgdgQOzcu5010RGtRVAT2W7yKxnrUHHZm7NTtoh0NDXdt44zg56v3xNeP31oAxkNwlZNioQj954-nwSViNmM6zmueQ5f-bC2lrpJn08I2IY-MPN71hiLxkmys4PIwhXPy3GmbZz1nJilGW9qLms4YGQt5kinh9uyxHJEVnsQiwccFHpPR7NSSc4DTc9szTWfBx5xWZLlFN10na9fGHWvr7xwcAQTyO1J1-sauVF1gVwk2xowFvcX80s0T3Dgc4A2fg74XvMHTlXu4A8-q0SUy7dSx8KDMB7ybL0XOBT5c6iv8ZxMox0wUA2VuQ4mE6_BYkYVYUnfs82QOMQdGcBfAFtxOVOKZni7NcGcctnwmhEnMJqC_QEdH55a8TCU1Yl9IBshZKnvbMYWxlz6fqdELedXqsM3xWS_oQ-iQhtKEGqRyH2bvdMjPCm41xqipH6J5bqVeYV-Tk4TUXpIBcYf3qff6_1t9vP3011Cg8zwLYD6r90rqe35XJ6h_S5Z95Y0ACEORUOdLVRdOnj3_XyQv5NDbU2ZKNjhg8q5DHw-AL57DK0j4WffMvq_ucKh5LLl3Q6cY0CJwYEBdTaxlJALyvKmT4hj-yBR5FncLPtW3w9WX3_B7ef4_ufFfN9xQnh8yGkGpnkEyb5-DWArdAS4drplEBvy5mYLlKUII5qQh8HtgQHmf8hB9Y9e1LM9WBoXRJVeHNzYuxvReH3zPidH683iV_u3KmtsWSKoGRFoOhEAaP8KZ47WCpYns8xZUAvDx5OIyWuMG6MM_VxrhC-zBGrdMYDXG8CZjR